{
  "video_id": "LIF5BnugxYM",
  "title": "Why Am I Even Alive? | Muniba Mazari Speech | Inspiring Women of Goalcast",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 20.0,
      "end_time": 2877.0,
      "text": "- I was 18 years old when I got married."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2877.0,
      "end_time": 5117.0,
      "text": "I belong to a very conservative family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5117.0,
      "end_time": 6986.0,
      "text": "a Baloch family, where"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 6986.0,
      "end_time": 10626.0,
      "text": "good daughters never\nsay no to their parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10626.0,
      "end_time": 12963.0,
      "text": "My father wanted me to get married,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 12963.0,
      "end_time": 14948.0,
      "text": "and all I said was, \"If\nthat makes you happy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 14948.0,
      "end_time": 16116.0,
      "text": "\"I will say yes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 16116.0,
      "end_time": 19866.0,
      "text": "And of course, it was\nnever a happy marriage."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 21438.0,
      "end_time": 25840.0,
      "text": "Just about after two\nyears of getting married,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25840.0,
      "end_time": 29507.0,
      "text": "about nine years ago,\nI made a car accident."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 32116.999999999996,
      "end_time": 34784.0,
      "text": "Somehow, my husband fell asleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36030.0,
      "end_time": 38530.0,
      "text": "and the car fell in the ditch."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40380.0,
      "end_time": 42466.0,
      "text": "He managed to jump out, saved himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42466.0,
      "end_time": 44547.0,
      "text": "I'm happy for him."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44547.0,
      "end_time": 46880.0,
      "text": "But I stayed inside the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48277.0,
      "end_time": 50282.0,
      "text": "and I sustained a lot of injuries."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50282.0,
      "end_time": 52072.0,
      "text": "The list is a bit long."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52072.0,
      "end_time": 54450.0,
      "text": "The radius and ulna of my\nright arm were fractured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54450.0,
      "end_time": 55625.0,
      "text": "the wrist was fractured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 55625.0,
      "end_time": 57857.0,
      "text": "shoulder bone and collar\nbone were fractured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 57857.0,
      "end_time": 59776.0,
      "text": "my whole ribcage got fractured."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 59776.0,
      "end_time": 61379.0,
      "text": "But that whole injury that changed me"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 61379.0,
      "end_time": 64936.0,
      "text": "and my life completely\nwas the spine injury."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 64936.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68321.0,
      "text": "Many people came to\nrescue, that gave me CPR,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 68321.0,
      "end_time": 70399.0,
      "text": "that dragged me out of the car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 70399.0,
      "end_time": 72732.0,
      "text": "and while they were dragging me out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 72732.0,
      "end_time": 75912.0,
      "text": "I got the complete\ntransaction of my spinal cord."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 75912.0,
      "end_time": 79258.0,
      "text": "Those two and a half months\nin the hospital were dreadful."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 79258.0,
      "end_time": 82373.0,
      "text": "I was at the verge of despair."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82373.0,
      "end_time": 84253.0,
      "text": "One day, a doctor came\ncame to me and he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 84253.0,
      "end_time": 86507.0,
      "text": "\"Well, I heard that you\nwanted to be an artist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 86507.0,
      "end_time": 88262.0,
      "text": "\"but you ended up being a housewife."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 88262.0,
      "end_time": 90804.0,
      "text": "\"I have bad news for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 90804.0,
      "end_time": 93050.0,
      "text": "\"You won't be able to paint again.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 93050.0,
      "end_time": 95821.0,
      "text": "The next day, the doctor\ncame to me and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 95821.0,
      "end_time": 98958.0,
      "text": "\"Your spine injury is so bad"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98958.0,
      "end_time": 101373.0,
      "text": "\"you won't be able to walk again.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101373.0,
      "end_time": 103863.0,
      "text": "I took a deep breath, and\nI said, \"It's all right.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 103863.0,
      "end_time": 105944.0,
      "text": "The next day, the doctor\ncame to me and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 105944.0,
      "end_time": 107209.0,
      "text": "\"Because of your spine injury"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107209.0,
      "end_time": 110067.0,
      "text": "\"and the fixation that\nyou have in your back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 110067.0,
      "end_time": 112810.0,
      "text": "\"you won't be able to give\nbirth to a child again.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 112810.0,
      "end_time": 114774.0,
      "text": "That day, I was devastated."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 114774.0,
      "end_time": 116768.0,
      "text": "I started to question my existence."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 116768.0,
      "end_time": 118435.0,
      "text": "Why am I even alive?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 119574.0,
      "end_time": 124308.0,
      "text": "So what kept me going was,\none day I asked my brothers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 124308.0,
      "end_time": 126022.0,
      "text": "\"I know I have a deformed hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126022.0,
      "end_time": 128549.0,
      "text": "\"but I'm tired of looking\nat these white walls"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 128549.0,
      "end_time": 131299.0,
      "text": "\"in the hospital, and\nwearing these white scrubs."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 131299.0,
      "end_time": 133851.0,
      "text": "\"Bring me some colors,\nbring me some small canvas."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133851.0,
      "end_time": 135351.0,
      "text": "\"I want to paint.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 136423.0,
      "end_time": 141316.0,
      "text": "So the very first painting\nI made was on my deathbed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 141316.0,
      "end_time": 143788.0,
      "text": "where I painted for the very first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 143788.0,
      "end_time": 145273.0,
      "text": "What an amazing therapy it was."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 145273.0,
      "end_time": 146945.0,
      "text": "Without uttering a single word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 146945.0,
      "end_time": 149653.0,
      "text": "I could paint my heart out."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 149653.0,
      "end_time": 152216.0,
      "text": "I could share my story."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 152216.0,
      "end_time": 155021.0,
      "text": "People used to come and\nsay, \"What lovely painting."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155021.0,
      "end_time": 156570.0,
      "text": "\"So much color!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 156570.0,
      "end_time": 159005.0,
      "text": "Nobody could see the grief in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 159005.0,
      "end_time": 160858.0,
      "text": "Only I could."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 160858.0,
      "end_time": 162701.0,
      "text": "And that day, I decided that"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 162701.0,
      "end_time": 165238.0,
      "text": "I'm going to live life for myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 165238.0,
      "end_time": 169153.0,
      "text": "I am not going to be that\nperfect person for someone."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 169153.0,
      "end_time": 170984.0,
      "text": "I am just going to take this moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 170984.0,
      "end_time": 173141.0,
      "text": "and I will make it perfect for myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 173141.0,
      "end_time": 175085.0,
      "text": "and I'm going to fight my fears."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 175085.0,
      "end_time": 179201.0,
      "text": "So, I wrote down, one\nby one, all those fears,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179201.0,
      "end_time": 181300.0,
      "text": "and I decided that I'm going\nto overcome those fears"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181300.0,
      "end_time": 182875.0,
      "text": "one at a time."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 182875.0,
      "end_time": 184951.0,
      "text": "You know what was my biggest fear?"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 184951.0,
      "end_time": 186323.0,
      "text": "Divorce."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 186323.0,
      "end_time": 190150.0,
      "text": "But the day I decided that\nthis is nothing but my fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 190150.0,
      "end_time": 193734.0,
      "text": "I liberated myself by setting him free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 193734.0,
      "end_time": 196554.0,
      "text": "and I made myself emotionally so strong"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 196554.0,
      "end_time": 198898.0,
      "text": "that the day I got the news\nthat he's getting married,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 198898.0,
      "end_time": 202134.0,
      "text": "I sent him a text that\nI'm so happy for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 202134.0,
      "end_time": 204268.0,
      "text": "and I wish you all the best."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 204268.0,
      "end_time": 207716.0,
      "text": "And he knows that I pray for him today."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 207716.0,
      "end_time": 211883.0,
      "text": "Number two was I won't be\nable to be a mother again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 212807.0,
      "end_time": 216099.0,
      "text": "and that was quite devastating for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 216099.0,
      "end_time": 217168.0,
      "text": "But then I realized, there are"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 217168.0,
      "end_time": 218897.0,
      "text": "so many children in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 218897.0,
      "end_time": 221625.0,
      "text": "All they want is acceptance."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 221625.0,
      "end_time": 223110.0,
      "text": "So there is no point of crying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 223110.0,
      "end_time": 226409.0,
      "text": "just go and adopt one,\nand that's what I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 226409.0,
      "end_time": 228659.0,
      "text": "(cheering)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 232670.0,
      "end_time": 234567.0,
      "text": "I gave my name in different organizations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 234567.0,
      "end_time": 238300.0,
      "text": "different orphanages,\nand I waited patiently."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 238300.0,
      "end_time": 240292.0,
      "text": "Two years later, I got this call from"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 240292.0,
      "end_time": 242309.0,
      "text": "a very small city in Pakistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 242309.0,
      "end_time": 244813.0,
      "text": "I got a call and they said,\n\"Are you Muniba Mazari?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 244813.0,
      "end_time": 247762.0,
      "text": "\"There is a baby boy, and\nwould you like to adopt?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 247762.0,
      "end_time": 249697.0,
      "text": "I could literally feel the labor pains."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 249697.0,
      "end_time": 252246.0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, I am going to adopt him!"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 252246.0,
      "end_time": 254663.0,
      "text": "I am coming to take him home."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 256119.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259514.00000000003,
      "text": "And that day, Neal was two days old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 259514.0,
      "end_time": 261097.0,
      "text": "and today he's six."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 263380.0,
      "end_time": 266254.0,
      "text": "You know when you end up\nbeing on the wheelchair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 266254.0,
      "end_time": 268156.0,
      "text": "what's the most painful thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 268156.0,
      "end_time": 269751.0,
      "text": "People think that they will"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 269751.0,
      "end_time": 271450.0,
      "text": "not be accepted by other people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 271450.0,
      "end_time": 275163.0,
      "text": "because we, in the world of\nperfect people, are imperfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 275163.0,
      "end_time": 278009.0,
      "text": "So I decided to appear more in public."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 278009.0,
      "end_time": 279683.0,
      "text": "I started to paint."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 279683.0,
      "end_time": 282002.0,
      "text": "I have done a lot of modeling campaigns."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 282002.0,
      "end_time": 283400.0,
      "text": "I decided that I'm going to join"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 283400.0,
      "end_time": 286087.0,
      "text": "the national TV of Pakistan\nas an anchor person."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 286087.0,
      "end_time": 287795.0,
      "text": "I became the National\nGlobal Goodwill Ambassador"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 287795.0,
      "end_time": 289388.0,
      "text": "for UN Women Pakistan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 289388.0,
      "end_time": 292486.0,
      "text": "and now I speak for the\nrights of women and children."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 292486.0,
      "end_time": 296470.0,
      "text": "I was featured in BBC 100 Women for 2015."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 296470.0,
      "end_time": 300053.0,
      "text": "I'm one of the Forbes\n30 Under 30 for 2016."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 301969.0,
      "end_time": 304939.0,
      "text": "So, when you accept\nyourself the way you are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 304939.0,
      "end_time": 307307.0,
      "text": "the world recognizes you."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 307307.0,
      "end_time": 310065.0,
      "text": "It all starts from within."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 310065.0,
      "end_time": 313398.0,
      "text": "We have this amazing fantasy about life."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 314391.0,
      "end_time": 316238.0,
      "text": "This is how things should work."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 316238.0,
      "end_time": 320184.0,
      "text": "This is my plan, it\nshould go as per my plan."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 320184.0,
      "end_time": 323581.0,
      "text": "If that doesn't happen, we give up."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 323581.0,
      "end_time": 326162.0,
      "text": "I never wanted to be on the wheelchair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 326162.0,
      "end_time": 329802.0,
      "text": "never thought of being on the wheelchair."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 329802.0,
      "end_time": 332006.0,
      "text": "This life is a test and a trail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 332006.0,
      "end_time": 334317.0,
      "text": "and the tests are never\nsupposed to be easy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 334317.0,
      "end_time": 336879.0,
      "text": "so when you're expecting ease from life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 336879.0,
      "end_time": 339446.0,
      "text": "and life gives you lemons,\nthen you make the lemonade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 339446.0,
      "end_time": 342273.0,
      "text": "and then do not blame life for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 342273.0,
      "end_time": 345856.0,
      "text": "It is okay to be scared,\nit is okay to cry."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 347620.0,
      "end_time": 352323.0,
      "text": "Everything is okay, but giving\nup should not be an option."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 352323.0,
      "end_time": 355441.0,
      "text": "They always say that\nfailure is not an option."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 355441.0,
      "end_time": 356801.0,
      "text": "Failure should be an option,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 356801.0,
      "end_time": 359523.0,
      "text": "because when you fail, you get up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 359523.0,
      "end_time": 361181.0,
      "text": "and then you fail, and then you get up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 361181.0,
      "end_time": 363292.0,
      "text": "and that keeps you going."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 363292.0,
      "end_time": 365727.0,
      "text": "Embrace each and every\nbreath that you are taking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 365727.0,
      "end_time": 368435.0,
      "text": "celebrate your life, live it."
